---
import Layout from '../layouts/main.astro';
import Header from '@/components/layout/Header';
import Footer from '@/components/layout/Footer';
import { Button } from '@/components/ui/button';
---

<Layout>
  <Header />
  <main>
    {/* Hero Section */}
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-indigo-50 to-white py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4">
        <div class="text-center">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">
            Frequently Asked Questions
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            Everything you need to know about IT security auditing with Audit Pro.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* FAQ Categories */}
    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="container mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
          <a href="#getting-started" class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-4">
              ðŸš€
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Getting Started</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Learn about our platform basics and how to begin your security audit journey.</p>
          </a>

          <a href="#platform-features" class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-4">
              âš¡
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Platform Features</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Discover the powerful features that make Audit Pro the leading security audit platform.</p>
          </a>

          <a href="#pricing-billing" class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-4">
              ðŸ’³
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Pricing & Billing</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Find answers about our pricing plans, billing cycles, and payment options.</p>
          </a>
        </div>

        {/* Getting Started Section */}
        <div id="getting-started" class="mb-16 scroll-mt-24">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8">Getting Started</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">How do I start using Audit Pro?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Sign up for a free 14-day trial to access all features. No credit card required. You can immediately start creating security audits, using our templates, and exploring the platform's capabilities. Check out our <a href="/best-practices" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Best Practices guide</a> to get started.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">What kind of support do you offer?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">We provide 24/7 expert support through chat, email, and phone. Enterprise customers get dedicated account managers and priority support. Visit our <a href="/help-center" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Help Center</a> for more details.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Do you offer training?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Yes, we provide comprehensive onboarding, video tutorials, documentation, and live training sessions for teams. Enterprise customers receive customized training programs. Browse our <a href="/ebooks" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">resource library</a> for training materials.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Platform Features Section */}
        <div id="platform-features" class="mb-16 scroll-mt-24">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8">Platform Features</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">What security standards do you support?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">We support all major security standards including ISO 27001, SOC 2, HIPAA, PCI DSS, and GDPR. Our templates are regularly updated to reflect the latest compliance requirements. Learn more in our <a href="/explore-industries" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">industry-specific guides</a>.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">How does the AI-powered analysis work?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Our AI analyzes your security controls, identifies gaps, and provides recommendations based on industry best practices and your specific compliance requirements. It continuously learns from new security threats and compliance updates.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Can I customize audit templates?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Yes, all audit templates are fully customizable. You can modify existing templates or create new ones from scratch to match your organization's specific needs and compliance requirements.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Pricing & Billing Section */}
        <div id="pricing-billing" class="mb-16 scroll-mt-24">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8">Pricing & Billing</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">How is pricing calculated?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Our pricing is based on the number of audits you conduct. Basic plans start at $49 per audit, while Pro plans offer more features at $99 per audit. Enterprise plans are customized based on your organization's needs. View our <a href="/pricing" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">detailed pricing</a> for more information.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Can I change plans anytime?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Yes, you can upgrade or downgrade your plan at any time. Changes take effect immediately, and billing is adjusted accordingly.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Do you offer refunds?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">We offer a 30-day money-back guarantee for all plans. If you're not satisfied with our service, contact our support team for a full refund.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Still Have Questions Section */}
    <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-100 to-blue-100">
      <div class="container mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">
          Still Have Questions?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Our team is here to help. Contact us for personalized assistance with your security auditing needs.
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
          <Button size="lg" className="bg-orange-500 hover:bg-orange-600 text-white">
            <a href="/help-center">Visit Help Center</a>
          </Button>
          <Button size="lg" variant="outline">
            <a href="/newsletter">Stay Updated</a>
          </Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  html {
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
  }
</style>
